title: Sannine
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Delivery, Take-out, Mexican, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A typical Middle Eastern food place, but they specifically list vegan / vegetarian options on the menu. The open kitchen is in the middle of the restaurant, and you can see your food being prepared. The chefs are accommodating and will explain what is in a dish. Prices are a little high for Mexico.
streetAddress: Juan Jose Baz 132, Centro Historico, Cuahtemoc
